it really depends what platform you're

00:01:20.500 --> 00:01:24.780
already working on and therefore the
platform from which you're extending.

00:01:24.780 --> 00:01:26.670
If you've already got an Android app,

00:01:26.670 --> 00:01:31.490
it can most easily be extended with a
lean back library to work on Android TV.

